  <description>
    <p>Tauon AI is a modern, AI-enhanced music player for your music collection. Based on Tauon Music Box, it adds intelligent playlist generation powered by Claude AI.</p>
    <p>AI Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Generate playlists from text descriptions using Claude AI</li>
      <li>Audio feature extraction and caching for intelligent matching</li>
      <li>Mood detection and classification</li>
      <li>Metadata enrichment with Last.fm genre lookup</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Standard Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Playback local audio files including MP3, FLAC and OGG</li>
      <li>Import Spotify tracks and manage Spotify playlists</li>
      <li>Add network tracks from Jellyfin, Airsonic and Plex servers</li>
      <li>Gapless playback</li>
      <li>Automatic CUE sheet detection</li>
      <li>Lookup artists on Rate Your Music and Bandcamp</li>
      <li>Support for last.fm and Listenbrainz</li>
      <li>Large album art and gallery layouts</li>
      <li>Multiple preset colour themes</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

